{"tid":2424763,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"休班警火炭籃球場打波放低銀包　連同警察委任證不翼而飛","createTime":"2021-02-27T00:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T02:28:26.000Z","uid":230530,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"70d80e69c1e027b4f69cae6144102b514cfc1ce4","tid":2424763,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:03:30.000Z","msg":"火炭發生休班警失竊案。周五（26日）晚上約8時，一名男子在山尾街一籃球場報案，據悉他打波期間，將銀包放於場上，未幾卻發現銀包不翼而飛，內有一張警察委任證及約300元現金。<br />\n警員接報趕抵，證實該名男子為休班警務人員；經初步調查後，將案件列作「盜竊」處理，交由沙田警區刑事調查隊接手跟進，暫時無人被捕。警方呼籲，市民如拾獲該張警察委任證，應立即致電999，或把委任證交到就近的警署。"},{"pid":"6d99a83682808a9d3895715e0bb348a334a55da0","tid":2424763,"uid":352936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"委任證唯一用途係咩唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ece916111b2e8d5ef8a149b1740231918d3ae29","tid":2424763,"uid":34410,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6d99a83682808a9d3895715e0bb348a334a55da0","tid":2424763,"uid":352936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"委任證唯一用途係咩唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:13:37.000Z","msg":"用途1: 叫雞唔俾錢"},{"pid":"f408c19c150e2f63ea3f4cda4ae1f9dcc851bb8d","tid":2424763,"uid":387001,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:14:37.000Z","msg":"唔見委任證應該會被處分<br />\n所以就安排被偷事件？"},{"pid":"a921b1c89a7295c5495c21550f0a511616e4becf","tid":2424763,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f408c19c150e2f63ea3f4cda4ae1f9dcc851bb8d","tid":2424763,"uid":387001,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:14:37.000Z","msg":"唔見委任證應該會被處分<br />\n所以就安排被偷事件？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:33:04.000Z","msg":"警：已強烈訓斥"},{"pid":"b02a6337855b5086b39abf408dde270f5e19a69c","tid":2424763,"uid":85461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:49:21.000Z","m